* &quot;Icarus at the Edge of Time&quot; (2008)
* &quot;The Fabric of the Cosmos: Space, Time, and the Texture of Reality&quot; (2004)
* &quot;The Elegant Universe: Superstrings, Hidden Dimensions, and the Quest for the Ultimate Theory&quot; (1999)

