* 1st Special Forces Operational Detachment-Delta (&quot;Delta Force&quot;)
* 10th Special Forces Group Special Forces Detachment &quot;A&quot;
* 75th Infantry Regiment (elements from 1st and 2nd Ranger Battalions)

